<font color="#FF0000">ALL THE TIME</font><br>
<tt>Wed Jul 30 18:27:44 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
De'Yona did decide to use birth control for a long period of time.  She just stopped for a while.  The really hard thing about birth control AND about std/AIDS control is that is has to be done all the time.  Also -- our partners may or may not be willing to go along with what we want to do.  Think about how many condom battles there probably are every day.  And about how many times we don't have condoms when we need them.<br><br>
It's tough to be consistent about this.  How many other things in life do we have to do all the time?  Some people are lucky.  They don't get pregnant or infected with anything.  Some of us live with consequences forever.  I don't want to nail De'Yona and others as if they never care.<br><br>

